<content type="html" xml:base="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=1531&amp;p=1645#p1645"><![CDATA[
What takes a person out of the Sunnah by Shaykh Ahmad An-Najjar £2.25<br /><br />to purchase go to<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.salafiri.bigcartel.com/product/what-takes-a-person-out-of-the-sunnah-shaykh-ahmad-an-najjar">http://www.salafiri.bigcartel.com/produ ... -an-najjar</a><!-- m --><br /><br />With Forwards by Shaykh Dr Salih bin Saad As-Suhaymi and Shaikh Dr Sulayman bin Saleemullah Ar-Ruhayli<br /><br />The Messenger of Allah Sallalahu Alayhi Wasallam said, upon you all is to follow my Sunnah and the Sunnah of the Rightly Guided Caliphs after me, bite on to it with your molars, Beware of newly invented matters, for indeed every newly invented matter is an innovation and every innovation is a misguidance.<br /><br />This is a researched based book which aids a persons understanding in how a person leave or exits the Sunnah and is no longer a Salafi. The book draws on the understanding of the earlier scholars and the Salaf us-Saleh. Th book serves and establishes a solid foundation in understanding this important concept in our times when there are those who are hasty in making tabdi of people as well as those who apply an all inclusive methodology of claiming everyone is upon the Sunnah.<br /><br />Translator: Isma'eel Beaumont <br />Publisher: T.I Publishing 2015 <br />Size: A5 <br />Pages: 68<dl class="file"><dt class="attach-image"><img src="https://forum.salafiri.com/download/file.php?id=142" class="postimage" alt="whats takes a person out of the Sunnah.jpg" onclick="viewableArea(this);" /></dt></dl><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=48">AbuKhuzaimahAnsari</a> — Mon Jan 08, 2018 1:36 pm</p><hr />
